OF THE DEAD GUY.

00:23:41.688 --> 00:23:43.918
MAYBE THERE REALLY IS
SOME KIND

00:23:43.956 --> 00:23:47.586
OF TWISTED LOVE-TRIANGLE THING
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

