T-SHIRT IN MY FACE,

00:24:28.000 --> 00:24:29.970
ADVERTISING HERSELF
AS A "STIMULUS PACKAGE."

00:24:30.002 --> 00:24:33.212
I DON'T NEED
ANY MORE STIMULI.

00:24:33.239 --> 00:24:35.879
Look, you can't just go around
accusing students

00:24:35.908 --> 00:24:37.708
of wanting to have sex
with you,

00:24:37.744 --> 00:24:39.314
especially not in front
of witnesses.

00:24:39.345 --> 00:24:40.745
WHAT WITNESSES?

00:24:40.780 --> 00:24:42.450
[ SCOFFS ]
ARE YOU REALLY THAT OBLIVIOUS?

00:24:42.481 --> 00:24:43.821
SHE WAS WITH A FRIEND.

00:24:43.850 --> 00:24:45.520
THAT'S WHO FILED
THE COMPLAINT.

00:24:45.552 --> 00:24:47.292
YOU'RE JOKING.
TELL ME YOU'RE...

00:24:47.319 --> 00:24:49.119
LOOK, DANIEL, I HAVE PUT UP
WITH ALL OF YOUR ECCENTRICITIES

00:24:49.155 --> 00:24:51.385
BECAUSE YOU ARE
A BRILLIANT SCHOLAR,

00:24:51.423 --> 00:24:53.893
YOU'RE A POPULAR TEACHER,
AND YOU'RE MY FRIEND.

00:24:53.926 --> 00:24:55.796
BUT HAVE YOU ANY IDEA

00:24:55.828 --> 00:24:59.228
WHAT KIND OF A HIT OUR ENDOWMENT
HAS TAKEN, HMM?

00:24:59.265 --> 00:25:01.265
WE CANNOT AFFORD
A LAWSUIT.

00:25:01.300 --> 00:25:03.740
WHAT ARE YOU
ASKING ME TO DO?

00:25:03.770 --> 00:25:06.540
HE WANTS ME TO APOLOGIZE --
TO BOTH GIRLS.

00:25:06.573 --> 00:25:08.643
[ CHUCKLES ]
IT'S OUTRAGEOUS!

00:25:08.675 --> 00:25:11.535
WHY ARE YOU SMILING?
WHAT, Y-YOU THINK THIS IS FUNNY?

00:25:11.578 --> 00:25:12.948
WHAT I THINK IS, IS THAT
YOU DEFLECTED THIS OFFER

00:25:12.979 --> 00:25:14.509
FROM THIS STUDENT
FOR THE SAME REASON

00:25:14.547 --> 00:25:16.677
YOU TURNED DOWN THE DINNER
INVITATION WITH KATE MORETTI.

00:25:16.716 --> 00:25:18.516
ENLIGHTEN ME.

00:25:18.551 --> 00:25:20.651
YOU ARE PETRIFIED OF
ANYTHING REMOTELY RESEMBLING

00:25:20.687 --> 00:25:22.817
AN INTIMATE CONNECTION
WITH ANOTHER HUMAN BEING.

00:25:22.855 --> 00:25:25.055
OH, SPARE ME
THE PSYCHOBABBLE.

00:25:25.091 --> 00:25:27.361
TELL ME I'M WRONG.

00:25:27.393 --> 00:25:29.363
NATALIE, LOOK AT ME.

00:25:29.395 --> 00:25:31.695
I-I-I HEAR VOICES.

00:25:31.731 --> 00:25:35.031
