I TALK TO THE WALLS.

00:25:37.970 --> 00:25:40.270
HOW AM I EVER GONNA HAVE

00:25:40.306 --> 00:25:43.976
AN INTIMATE CONNECTION
WITH ANYBODY?

00:25:45.511 --> 00:25:46.851
YOU HAD AN INCIDENT.

00:25:48.347 --> 00:25:50.047
DANIEL?

00:25:56.222 --> 00:25:57.592
WELL,
SOMETIMES THIS HAPPENS.

00:25:57.624 --> 00:25:59.094
YOU DEAL WITH IT,
AND YOU MOVE ON.

00:25:59.125 --> 00:26:02.025
[ SCOFFS ]
RIGHT.

00:26:02.061 --> 00:26:04.701
SO, WHY IS IT
THAT I GET THE FEELING

00:26:04.731 --> 00:26:06.701
THAT YOU'RE MORE WORRIED
ABOUT THIS THAN USUAL?

00:26:09.435 --> 00:26:13.435
WHAT IF NEXT TIME
IT HAPPENS IN FRONT OF KATE?

00:26:14.641 --> 00:26:17.911
YOU TOLD KATE ABOUT
YOUR CONDITION A LONG TIME AGO.

00:26:17.944 --> 00:26:23.024
WELL, KNOWING AND SEEING
ARE TWO DIFFERENT THINGS.

00:26:25.251 --> 00:26:28.921
I DON'T -- M-MAYBE
I SHOULD GET OFF THIS CASE.

00:26:28.955 --> 00:26:32.155
QUIT WITHOUT SOLVING IT?
THEN YOU'D REALLY GO CRAZY.

00:26:33.926 --> 00:26:37.056
HAVE YOU TALKED TO ROSENTHAL
ABOUT GOING BACK ON YOUR MEDS?

00:26:37.096 --> 00:26:38.866
NO, NO.

00:26:38.898 --> 00:26:41.898
WE'VE TALKED -- LOOK, FOR SOME
PEOPLE, THEY'RE A MIRACLE --

00:26:41.934 --> 00:26:43.144
N-NOT ME.

00:26:43.169 --> 00:26:45.339
BUT YOU HAD
FEWER SYMPTOMS.

00:26:45.371 --> 00:26:47.711
AND I COULDN'T CONCENTRATE
LONG ENOUGH

00:26:47.740 --> 00:26:49.210
TO FINISH A [BLEEP] SODOKU.

00:26:49.241 --> 00:26:51.411
I COULDN'T WRITE.
I COULDN'T WORK.

00:26:51.443 --> 00:26:54.583
NO, NO, NO.
I-I CAN HANDLE THIS, NAT.

00:26:54.613 --> 00:26:58.753
I JUST -- I'LL KEEP UP
MY TALK THERAPY WITH ROSENTHAL.

00:26:58.785 --> 00:27:02.515
I-I'LL STICK TO MY ROUTINE.
I'LL WATCH MY DIET.

00:27:02.554 --> 00:27:05.734
I'LL KEEP MY MIND FOCUSED
AND OCCUPIED.

00:27:05.758 --> 00:27:08.088
OKAY. WELL,
LET'S FOCUS ON THE INCIDENT.

00:27:08.127 --> 00:27:09.157
TELL ME ABOUT IT.

00:27:09.195 --> 00:27:10.525
WHAT IS THERE TO TELL?

00:27:10.562 --> 00:27:12.632
IT WAS A SCHIZOPHRENIC
HALLUCINATION.

00:27:12.665 --> 00:27:15.265
IT WAS THE PRODUCT
OF RANDOMLY FIRING NEURONS.

00:27:15.301 --> 00:27:17.471
DANIEL, YOU KNOW
HOW YOUR MIND WORKS.

00:27:17.503 --> 00:27:19.543
SOMETIMES THESE HALLUCINATIONS
TELL YOU THINGS

00:27:19.571 --> 00:27:21.571
THAT YOUR CONSCIOUS MIND
CAN'T MAKE SENSE OF.

00:27:24.110 --> 00:27:26.610
TELL ME WHAT YOU SAW.

00:27:31.984 --> 00:27:34.124
THE MAN.

00:27:34.153 --> 00:27:36.623
HE WORKS AT TechSan,
THEN HE CAME TO MY HOUSE,

00:27:36.655 --> 00:27:38.185
SAID HE WAS THE KILLER,

00:27:38.224 --> 00:27:40.394
WHICH I'M PRETTY SURE
IS PHYSICALLY IMPOSSIBLE.

00:27:40.426 --> 00:27:42.086
WHAT ELSE DID HE SAY?

00:27:46.866 --> 00:27:51.666
THAT VALERIE NELSON
IS A LIAR.

00:27:51.704 --> 00:27:52.814
WHO IS SHE?

00:27:54.741 --> 00:27:56.981
SHE WAS HAVING AN AFFAIR
WITH THE VICTIM.

00:27:58.344 --> 00:28:01.814
SHE SAYS SHE HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH THE CRIME.

00:28:01.848 --> 00:28:05.318
AND THE POLICE
BELIEVE HER.

00:28:05.351 --> 00:28:08.651
WELL, IF SHE'S LYING...

00:28:08.687 --> 00:28:10.617
HOW COULD YOU PROVE IT?

00:28:10.656 --> 00:28:14.986
THE INTERNATIONAL ATOMIC ENERGY
AGENCY CONFIRMED IN THE 1990s

00:28:15.027 --> 00:28:16.727
THAT SADDAM HUSSEIN

00:28:16.763 --> 00:28:19.333
HAD AN ADVANCED NUCLEAR WEAPONS
DEVELOPMENT PROGRAM.

00:28:19.365 --> 00:28:21.325
WHY ARE YOU MAKING ME RELIVE
THIS NIGHTMARE?

00:28:21.367 --> 00:28:22.737
JUST WATCH.

00:28:22.769 --> 00:28:24.299
...HAD A DESIGN
FOR A NUCLEAR WEAPON

00:28:24.336 --> 00:28:26.106
AND WAS WORKING
ON FIVE DIFFERENT METHODS

00:28:26.138 --> 00:28:28.108
OF ENRICHING URANIUM
FOR A BOMB.

00:28:28.140 --> 00:28:30.040
THE BRITISH GOVERNMENT
HAS LEARNED

00:28:30.076 --> 00:28:32.536
THAT SADDAM HUSSEIN RECENTLY
SOUGHT SIGNIFICANT QUANTITIES

00:28:32.578 --> 00:28:33.678
OF URANIUM FROM AFRICA.

00:28:33.712 --> 00:28:36.022
[ LAUGHING ]

00:28:37.583 --> 00:28:40.723
INTELLIGENCE SOURCES TELL US
THAT HE HAS ATTEMPTED TO...

00:28:40.753 --> 00:28:44.193
THANK YOU, JIMMY.

00:28:44.223 --> 00:28:45.893
JIMMY'S AN APHASIAC.

00:28:45.925 --> 00:28:48.755
HE'S LOST THE ABILITY TO
COMPREHEND SPOKEN LANGUAGE.

00:28:48.795 --> 00:28:51.625
TO COMPENSATE, MANY APHASIACS
BECOME HIGHLY SENSITIVE

00:28:51.663 --> 00:28:53.573
TO SUBTLE INFLECTIONS
IN SPEECH.

00:28:53.599 --> 00:28:54.999
NOW, WHEN WE LIE,

00:28:55.034 --> 00:28:57.144
THOSE VOCAL NUANCES
BECOME MORE PRONOUNCED.

00:28:57.169 --> 00:28:59.669
MOST OF US WOULDN'T NOTICE,
BUT APHASIACS DO.

00:28:59.705 --> 00:29:02.265
AND FOR SOME REASON,
TO THEM, IT SOUNDS FUNNY.

00:29:02.308 --> 00:29:05.208
HE'S A HUMAN LIE DETECTOR.

00:29:05.244 --> 00:29:06.414
NOW, P-PUT THAT IN.

00:29:09.181 --> 00:29:10.521
YOU'RE DOING GREAT.

00:29:16.055 --> 00:29:18.355
Hammond: SO, WHERE WERE YOU
ON THE NIGHT OF MARCH 5th?

00:29:18.390 --> 00:29:22.760
HOME...
WAITING FOR CLARK TO CALL.

00:29:22.795 --> 00:29:24.555
[ LAUGHING ]

00:29:24.596 --> 00:29:28.296
IT WAS THE NIGHT HE WAS GONNA
TELL PAMELA HE WAS LEAVING.

00:29:39.812 --> 00:29:43.322
MS. NELSON,
AGENT MORETTI, FBI.

00:29:51.858 --> 00:29:53.888
M[ GROANS ]!

00:29:53.926 --> 00:29:56.256
VALERIE? VALERIE?

00:30:00.933 --> 00:30:02.733
I NEED AN AMBULANCE.

00:30:07.739 --> 00:30:09.479
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

00:30:12.178 --> 00:30:14.478
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

00:30:14.513 --> 00:30:16.483
PROBERT!

00:30:16.515 --> 00:30:18.415
THINK SHE'S
GONNA MAKE IT?

00:30:18.450 --> 00:30:19.790
IT'S TOO EARLY TO SAY.

00:30:19.818 --> 00:30:22.088
VICIOUS BLOW TO THE BACK
OF THE HEAD LIKE THAT?

00:30:22.121 --> 00:30:24.761
SHE MIGHT NOT EVEN
HAVE SEEN HER ATTACKER.

00:30:24.790 --> 00:30:26.830
WHY ARE WE STILL
ON THIS CASE?

00:30:26.859 --> 00:30:29.229
CHICAGO P.D.
SHOULD BE HANDLING IT.

00:30:29.261 --> 00:30:32.161
JUST FIND OUT
WHO SHE'S BEEN TALKING TO.

00:30:33.765 --> 00:30:36.235
WHAT'S THE NATURE OF YOUR
RELATIONSHIP WITH MS. NELSON?

00:30:36.268 --> 00:30:37.868
I COULDN'T HAVE PICKED HER OUT
OF THE CROWD

00:30:37.904 --> 00:30:39.114
AT THE COMPANY PICNIC.

00:30:39.138 --> 00:30:40.468
THEN WHY THE CALLS?

00:30:40.506 --> 00:30:41.936
WE CAME DOWN HERE
VOLUNTARILY.

00:30:41.974 --> 00:30:43.444
MR. KLANE ISN'T
UNDER ANY OBLIGATION

00:30:43.475 --> 00:30:44.835
TO ANSWER THESE QUESTIONS.

00:30:44.877 --> 00:30:46.347
WERE YOU AWARE THAT VALERIE
WAS HAVING AN AFFAIR

00:30:46.378 --> 00:30:47.678
WITH YOUR DEAD
GENERAL COUNSEL?

00:30:47.713 --> 00:30:49.823
WHAT DOES THAT HAVE TO DO
WITH ME?

00:30:49.848 --> 00:30:52.148
MAYBE CLARK WEILMAN
WASN'T THE ONLY ONE

00:30:52.184 --> 00:30:55.354
GETTING EXECUTIVE PERKS
FROM VALERIE.

00:30:55.387 --> 00:30:58.857
MAYBE YOU FOUND OUT,
GOT JEALOUS, KILLED CLARK,

00:30:58.891 --> 00:31:00.461
AND THEN YOU TRIED TO DO
THE SAME THING TO VALERIE.

00:31:00.492 --> 00:31:02.132
WHAT?!
WE'RE DONE HERE.

00:31:02.161 --> 00:31:04.861
THAT'S OKAY. WE'VE GOT
HER HARD DRIVES, E-MAILS.

00:31:04.897 --> 00:31:06.527
EVEN IF SHE DOESN'T
SURVIVE THIS SURGERY,

00:31:06.565 --> 00:31:08.625
WE WILL FIND OUT
WHAT THE TWO OF YOU WERE UP TO.

00:31:08.667 --> 00:31:11.167
OKAY, PHILIP,
SIT, SIT, IT'S FINE.

00:31:11.203 --> 00:31:14.813
CHAMOMILE.
NO MILK, NO SUGAR.

00:31:14.840 --> 00:31:16.210
AFTER CLARK WAS KILLED,

00:31:16.242 --> 00:31:17.982
I GOT AN E-MAIL
FROM MS. VALERIE

00:31:18.010 --> 00:31:20.180
SAYING IT WAS URGENT
I SHOULD CALL HER, SO I DID.

00:31:20.212 --> 00:31:21.352
YOU'RE WELCOME.

