SHE SAID SHE HAD INFORMATION

00:31:22.748 --> 00:31:23.648
THAT COULD BE DAMAGING
TO THE COMPANY.

00:31:23.682 --> 00:31:25.722
WHAT KIND OF INFORMATION?

00:31:25.751 --> 00:31:28.321
SOMETHING ABOUT ANOMALOUS
STUDY RESULTS FOR ONE
OF OUR PRODUCTS.

00:31:28.354 --> 00:31:29.694
SHE SAID SHE DIDN'T WANT TO
TA Gerard: DON'T DRINK THAT. E.

00:31:29.721 --> 00:31:31.621
WHAT TIME?

00:31:31.657 --> 00:31:33.957
IT MIGHT KILL YOU.

00:31:35.727 --> 00:31:37.557
[ GASPS ]

