ARE YOU TRYING
TO POISON ME?!

00:31:39.698 --> 00:31:41.798
I TOLD YOU,
NO MILK, NO SUGAR.

00:31:41.833 --> 00:31:44.743
COME ON, DOC.
THAT'S THE TEA?ER WEAPON.

00:31:44.770 --> 00:31:45.770
YEAH, IT'S TEA.

00:31:47.473 --> 00:31:49.543
NOT TEA -- POISON.
REMEMBER TIMOTHY MAY?

00:31:49.575 --> 00:31:51.205
SAID HIS MOTHER
WAS POISONED.

00:31:51.243 --> 00:31:53.453
I POISONED HER...
AND KILLED CLARK WEILMAN.

00:31:53.479 --> 00:31:55.449
WHAT'S TO UNDERSTAND?

00:31:55.481 --> 00:31:57.021
SHE'S TRYING TO
ESTABLISH MOTIVE.

00:31:57.049 --> 00:31:58.679
I'LL GIVE YOU A MOTIVE.

00:31:58.717 --> 00:32:00.247
SHE WAS GOING TO EXPOSE ME,
AND NOW THAT'S YOUR JOB.

00:32:00.286 --> 00:32:01.846
HOW?

00:32:01.887 --> 00:32:03.987
CAN YOU BE QUIET, PLEASE?
I'M TRYING TO LISTEN.

00:32:07.226 --> 00:32:10.426
AAH!
WHAT THE [BLEEP]

00:32:10.462 --> 00:32:12.102
I JUST BOUGHT THIS SUIT!

00:32:12.131 --> 00:32:13.631
SORRY. TRY CLUB SODA.

00:32:18.304 --> 00:32:21.574
YOU'VE HAD A GUT FEELING
ALL THIS TIME, HAVEN'T YOU,

00:32:21.607 --> 00:32:23.407
ESPECIALLY AFTER WHAT
TIMOTHY MAY SAID ABOUT HIS MOM

00:32:23.442 --> 00:32:24.882
AND WHAT THOSE PEOPLE
AT TechSan CLAIMED

00:32:24.910 --> 00:32:25.910
ABOUT THE INSULPRIN STUDY.

00:32:25.944 --> 00:32:27.884
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

00:32:27.913 --> 00:32:29.123
DON'T YOU REMEMBER
MY NAME?

00:32:29.148 --> 00:32:31.118
GERARD PERMUT.
SO WHAT?

00:32:31.150 --> 00:32:32.920
SO, I KNOW HOW MUCH
YOU LIKE PUZZLES.

00:32:32.951 --> 00:32:35.991
IT'S ANOTHER ANAGRAM.

00:33:10.156 --> 00:33:12.956
I SOLVED IT.

