00:33:16.528 --> 00:33:21.298
Kate: "GERARD PERMUT.
DRUG TAMPERER."

00:33:21.333 --> 00:33:22.633
WHO'S GERARD PERMUT?

00:33:22.668 --> 00:33:24.038
YOU WROTE ON THE WALL?

00:33:24.070 --> 00:33:25.470
I THINK
SOMEBODY TAMPERED

00:33:25.504 --> 00:33:26.644
WITH THE RESULTS
OF THE INSULPRIN STUDY.

00:33:26.672 --> 00:33:27.812
WHAT MAKES YOU SAY THAT?

00:33:27.839 --> 00:33:29.309
GUT FEELING.

00:33:29.341 --> 00:33:31.811
TIMOTHY MAY BELIEVED HIS MOTHER
WAS POISONED,

00:33:31.843 --> 00:33:33.483
THAT HER HEART ATTACK WAS CAUSED
BY THE MEDICATION.

00:33:33.512 --> 00:33:34.682
TIMOTHY MAY IS PARANOID.

00:33:34.713 --> 00:33:36.123
THAT DOESN'T
MAKE HIM WRONG.

