MAY'S MOTHER
WAS TAKING A PLACEBO.

00:33:37.583 --> 00:33:39.323
ACCORDING TO THE DATA
REPORTED BY THE COMPANY.

00:33:39.351 --> 00:33:40.791
WHICH YOU BELIEVE
WAS TAMPERED WITH.

00:33:40.819 --> 00:33:43.189
