THE COMPANY BILLIONS

00:33:43.222 --> 00:33:45.362
TO PULL THAT DRUG
OFF THE MARKET.

00:33:45.391 --> 00:33:48.331
C.E.O. WOULD CERTAINLY HAVE
MOTIVE TO COVER THAT UP.

00:33:48.360 --> 00:33:49.930
MAYBE.

00:33:49.961 --> 00:33:53.801
BUT WHO HAD DIRECT ACCESS
TO THE STUDY RESULTS?

00:33:58.870 --> 00:34:00.670
Kate: DR. BRYANT.

00:34:00.706 --> 00:34:02.836
AGENT MORETTI.
DR. PIERCE.

00:34:02.874 --> 00:34:05.844
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

00:34:05.877 --> 00:34:07.147
WE ARE TRYING TO FIGURE OUT

00:34:07.179 --> 00:34:08.509
WHO TRIED TO KILL
VALERIE NELSON.

00:34:08.547 --> 00:34:11.347
WE FOUND THESE
ON HER HARD DRIVE.

00:34:11.383 --> 00:34:15.393
WE WERE HOPING MAYBE YOU COULD
TELL US WHAT THEY ARE.

00:34:15.421 --> 00:34:18.021
WELL, THESE LOOK LIKE
STUDY RESULTS

00:34:18.056 --> 00:34:19.456
OF MORBIDITY RATES.

00:34:19.491 --> 00:34:21.291
RIGHT,
FROM YOUR INSULPRIN TRIAL,

00:34:21.327 --> 00:34:24.027
EXCEPT THEY SHOW AN UNUSUALLY
HIGH INCIDENCE OF HEART ATTACK

00:34:24.062 --> 00:34:26.202
AMONG WOMEN PARTICIPATING
IN THE STUDY.

00:34:26.232 --> 00:34:28.732
YEAH, WELL, THERE --
THERE MUST BE A MISTAKE.

00:34:28.767 --> 00:34:30.397
WHAT ABOUT THIS ONE?

00:34:31.737 --> 00:34:33.537
AH, YES.
THESE ARE THE CORRECT RESULTS.

00:34:33.572 --> 00:34:35.312
AH. YOU SEE HERE?

00:34:35.341 --> 00:34:37.481
THE INCIDENCE OF HEART ATTACKS
IS APPROXIMATELY THE SAME

00:34:37.509 --> 00:34:38.679
FOR THOSE TAKING THE PLACEBO

00:34:38.710 --> 00:34:40.310
AS FOR THOSE
TAKING THE REAL DRUG.

00:34:40.346 --> 00:34:42.676
BUT ONLY BECAUSE SOMEBODY
TAMPERED WITH THESE RESULTS.

00:34:42.714 --> 00:34:45.384
THEY MOVED PATIENT NAMES
FROM ONE GROUP INTO THE OTHER.

00:34:45.417 --> 00:34:47.817
COME ON.
WHO'D DO SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

00:34:47.853 --> 00:34:50.563
DR. PIERCE TELLS ME

00:34:50.589 --> 00:34:53.019
THAT PHARMACOLOGISTS
OF YOUR STATURE

00:34:53.058 --> 00:34:54.728
GET PRETTY SWEET DEALS --

00:34:54.760 --> 00:34:57.400
SHARED PATENTS
ON THE DRUGS YOU DEVELOP.

00:34:57.429 --> 00:34:58.999
WHAT ARE YOU
TRYING TO SAY?

00:34:59.030 --> 00:35:01.200
VALERIE FOUND OUT YOU WERE
FALSIFYING THE STUDY,

00:35:01.233 --> 00:35:04.343
SO SHE WENT TO HER BOYFRIEND,
TechSan's TOP LAWYER.

00:35:04.370 --> 00:35:06.340
THEY WERE GONNA RUIN EVERYTHING
THAT YOU HAD WORKED FOR,

00:35:06.372 --> 00:35:07.512
SO YOU HAD TO STOP THEM.

00:35:07.539 --> 00:35:08.909
[ SCOFFS ]
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

00:35:08.940 --> 00:35:09.910
SIZE 10 BROGANS?

00:35:09.941 --> 00:35:12.411
YOUR SHOES.

00:35:14.112 --> 00:35:17.152
YOU LEFT A BLOODY FOOTPRINT
IN VALERIE'S APARTMENT.

00:35:32.598 --> 00:35:34.668
YOU SPEND
YOUR WHOLE CAREER

00:35:34.700 --> 00:35:36.440
LOOKING FOR THAT
ONE MIRACLE CURE, YOU KNOW?

00:35:37.936 --> 00:35:40.406
THIS WASN'T ABOUT MONEY FOR YOU.
IT WAS ABOUT SCIENCE.

00:35:40.439 --> 00:35:42.239
YOU UNDERSTAND,
DR. PIERCE.

00:35:42.274 --> 00:35:44.244
EVERY DRUG
HAS SIDE EFFECTS.

00:35:44.276 --> 00:35:46.776
I FIGURED OUT WHY IT WAS CAUSING
THE HEART ATTACKS.

00:35:46.812 --> 00:35:48.752
I COULD HAVE WORKED OUT
THE KINKS...

00:35:48.780 --> 00:35:51.380
BUT VALERIE STARTED
COLLECTING EVIDENCE AGAINST ME

00:35:51.417 --> 00:35:52.477
LIKE I'M A CRIMINAL.

00:35:52.518 --> 00:35:53.988
YOU MEAN
THE STUDY RESULTS.

00:35:54.019 --> 00:35:55.649
YES.

00:35:55.687 --> 00:35:57.687
AND THEN I SAW HER
STEALING PILLS...

00:36:02.994 --> 00:36:04.534
SO I FOLLOWED HER.

00:36:10.001 --> 00:36:12.641
SHE BROUGHT THEM TO CLARK.

00:36:14.873 --> 00:36:17.283
SHE GOES TO A LAWYER
INSTEAD OF ME?!

00:36:17.309 --> 00:36:18.679
YOU FIGURED
THAT THEY WERE GOING

00:36:18.710 --> 00:36:20.310
TO GET THE PILLS
INDEPENDENTLY TESTED,

00:36:20.346 --> 00:36:22.146
PROVE THAT
THEY WERE DANGEROUS.

00:36:22.180 --> 00:36:24.480
I THOUGHT...

00:36:24.516 --> 00:36:26.316
IF I COULD JUST
MAKE HIM UNDERSTAND.

00:36:26.352 --> 00:36:28.692
CLARK, I DON'T KNOW WHAT
VALERIE'S BEEN TELLING YOU,

00:36:28.720 --> 00:36:29.820
BUT I CAN FIX THIS.

00:36:29.855 --> 00:36:31.115
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
THE LIABILITY

00:36:31.156 --> 00:36:32.286
YOU'VE EXPOSED
THIS COMPANY TO?

00:36:32.324 --> 00:36:33.734
CLARK, PLEASE!

00:36:33.759 --> 00:36:35.859
GET OUT OF HERE
BEFORE I GET THE POLICE!

00:36:39.365 --> 00:36:41.365
OHH!

00:36:44.035 --> 00:36:46.265
[ GRUNTING ]

00:36:47.839 --> 00:36:50.839
I GUESS...

00:36:52.544 --> 00:36:54.884
I GUESS I WENT
A LITTLE CRAZY.

00:36:57.883 --> 00:37:00.523
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

00:37:00.552 --> 00:37:02.522
NICE WORK, DETECTIVE.

00:37:02.554 --> 00:37:03.864
Hammond: PSYCHO.

00:37:03.889 --> 00:37:05.019
YOU DIDN'T TELL ME
YOU FOUND A FOOTPRINT

00:37:05.056 --> 00:37:06.016
IN VALERIE'S APARTMENT.

00:37:06.057 --> 00:37:07.187
I DIDN'T.

00:37:07.225 --> 00:37:11.195
DETECTIVE MORETTI,
I AM SHOCKED

00:37:11.229 --> 00:37:13.029
THAT YOU WOULD
SO BLATANTLY MANIPULATE

00:37:13.064 --> 00:37:15.204
AN OBVIOUSLY TROUBLED
INDIVIDUAL.

00:37:17.068 --> 00:37:18.798
Gerard:
WHAT'S UP, DOC?

00:37:20.372 --> 00:37:23.342
DANIEL, WHAT IS IT?

00:37:23.375 --> 00:37:25.335
IT'S NOTHING.
[ CHUCKLES ]

00:37:25.377 --> 00:37:27.177
NO, IT'S NOT NOTHING.

00:37:27.212 --> 00:37:28.652
YOU CAUGHT THE KILLER.

00:37:28.680 --> 00:37:31.720
SO, WHAT THE [BLEEP]
AM I STILL DOING HERE?

00:37:34.420 --> 00:37:36.220
CASE ISN'T OVER YET.

00:37:36.254 --> 00:37:38.224
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

00:37:40.426 --> 00:37:42.726
DANIEL?

00:37:45.130 --> 00:37:46.930
DR. BRYANT!

00:37:46.965 --> 00:37:48.095
WHAT NOW?

00:37:48.133 --> 00:37:49.403
YOU SAID
YOU FIGURED OUT WHY

00:37:49.435 --> 00:37:51.165
INSULPRIN WAS
CAUSING HEART ATTACKS.

00:37:51.202 --> 00:37:53.172
WHAT WAS IT?

00:37:53.204 --> 00:37:57.014
THE DRUG WAS DEPLETING
PATIENTS' THIAMINE LEVELS.

00:37:57.042 --> 00:38:00.012
DANIEL,
WHAT IS GOING ON?

00:38:00.045 --> 00:38:02.105
THERE'S ANOTHER VICTIM.

00:38:07.085 --> 00:38:10.755
I RAN THE SECOND TOX SCREEN
YOU ASKED FOR.

00:38:10.789 --> 00:38:13.089
WE FOUND SIGNIFICANT LEVELS
OF CONCANAVALIN A.

00:38:13.124 --> 00:38:15.434
THE PRIMARY SUGAR-BINDING
MOLECULE IN INSULPRIN.

00:38:15.461 --> 00:38:17.101
"SHE'S JUST A EXCUSE ME?

00:38:17.128 --> 00:38:18.558
YOU WERE RIGHT, HARVEY.

00:38:18.597 --> 00:38:20.197
PAMELA WEILMAN ISN'T BULIMIC.
SHE'S JUST THIN.

00:38:20.231 --> 00:38:22.031
IT WAS INSULPRIN
THAT DEPLETED HER THIAMINE.

00:38:22.067 --> 00:38:23.267
IF MRS. WEILMAN
WASN'T DIABETIC,

00:38:23.301 --> 00:38:24.841
WHY WOULD SHE BE
ON A DIABETES DRUG?

00:38:24.870 --> 00:38:26.140
I DON'T THINK SHE KNEW
SHE WAS TAKING IT.

00:38:26.171 --> 00:38:27.541
I THINK
SHE WAS BEING POISONED.

00:38:27.573 --> 00:38:28.973
SOMEONE MUST HAVE BEEN
PUTTING IT IN HER FOOD,

00:38:29.007 --> 00:38:30.307
TRYING TO INDUCE
A HEART ATTACK.

00:38:30.342 --> 00:38:31.582
BUT SHE DIDN'T HAVE
A HEART ATTACK.

00:38:31.610 --> 00:38:33.480
BECAUSE SIDE EFFECTS
MANIFEST DIFFERENTLY

00:38:33.512 --> 00:38:34.952
IN DIFFERENT PATIENTS.

00:38:34.980 --> 00:38:36.720
LOW THIAMINE LEVELS
CAN CAUSE CARDIAC FAILURE,

00:38:36.748 --> 00:38:38.718
BUT IN RARE INSTANCES,
THEY CAN ALSO CAUSE...

00:38:38.750 --> 00:38:40.190
KORSAKOFF'S SYNDROME.

00:38:42.521 --> 00:38:43.791
WAIT.
SO WHO WAS POISONING HER?

00:38:47.759 --> 00:38:51.059
MS. NELSON?
I'M AGENT MORETTI, FBI.

00:38:51.096 --> 00:38:52.626
THIS IS DR. PIERCE.

00:38:52.664 --> 00:38:54.234
WOULD YOU MIND IF I ASKED YOU
A COUPLE QUESTIONS

00:38:54.265 --> 00:38:56.325
FOR OUR CASE
AGAINST DR. BRYANT?

00:38:56.368 --> 00:39:00.068
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
HE TRIED TO KILL ME.

00:39:00.105 --> 00:39:01.735
WELL, YOU FOUND OUT

00:39:01.773 --> 00:39:05.243
HE WAS TAMPERING
WITH THE INSULPRIN STUDY,

00:39:05.276 --> 00:39:07.006
SO YOU TOLD CLARK WEILMAN
ABOUT YOUR SUSPICIONS?

00:39:07.045 --> 00:39:09.575
I KNEW THAT DRUG
WAS GONNA HURT A LOT OF PEOPLE

00:39:09.615 --> 00:39:10.845
WHEN IT HIT THE MARKET.

00:39:10.882 --> 00:39:12.152
CLARK WAS A LAWYER.

00:39:12.183 --> 00:39:14.393
I-I FIGURED
HE'D KNOW WHAT TO DO.

00:39:14.420 --> 00:39:17.990
SO HE TOLD YOU
YOU NEEDED MORE EVIDENCE?

00:39:18.023 --> 00:39:19.963
THAT'S WHY YOU BROUGHT HIM
THE PILLS?

00:39:19.991 --> 00:39:22.791
CLARK DIDN'T WANT TO EXPOSE
THE COMPANY TO ANY LIABILITY

00:39:22.828 --> 00:39:24.128
UNLESS HE KNEW FOR SURE

00:39:24.162 --> 00:39:26.002
DR. BRYANT HAD DONE
SOMETHING WRONG.

00:39:26.031 --> 00:39:27.331
[ SCOFFS ]

00:39:27.365 --> 00:39:28.895
WHAT?

00:39:28.934 --> 00:39:31.174
IT'S JUST FUNNY YOU DIDN'T TELL
THE POLICE ANY OF THIS.

00:39:31.202 --> 00:39:33.542
T-THEY WANTED TO KNOW ABOUT
MY RELATIONSHIP WITH CLARK.

00:39:33.572 --> 00:39:35.772
I DIDN'T THINK IT HAD ANYTHING
TO DO WITH THE DRUG.

00:39:35.807 --> 00:39:36.977
OH, COME ON.

00:39:37.008 --> 00:39:38.278
YOU GAVE CLARK WEILMAN
THOSE PILLS

00:39:38.309 --> 00:39:40.049
SO HE COULD POISON
HIS WIFE, RIGHT?

00:39:40.078 --> 00:39:41.408
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR MIND?

00:39:41.447 --> 00:39:42.607
WELL, THAT'S NOT
THE CLINICAL DESCRIPTION,

00:39:42.648 --> 00:39:44.048
BUT YES, ACTUALLY.

00:39:44.082 --> 00:39:46.722
AND POOR DR. BRYANT --
HE WAS OUT OF HIS MIND, TOO.

00:39:46.752 --> 00:39:48.652
HE WAS FEELING SO GUILTY
FOR WHAT HE'D DONE

00:39:48.687 --> 00:39:49.887
THAT HE BECAME PARANOID,

00:39:49.921 --> 00:39:51.391
AND HE MADE
THE SAME MISTAKE WE DID.

00:39:51.423 --> 00:39:53.633
HE ASSUMED THAT YOU'D STOLEN
THOSE PILLS AS EVIDENCE

00:39:53.659 --> 00:39:55.159
WHEN IN FACT YOU WERE SUPPLYING
CLARK WEILMAN

00:39:55.193 --> 00:39:56.293
WITH THE PERFECT
MURDER WEAPON.

00:39:56.327 --> 00:39:57.627
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

00:39:57.663 --> 00:39:59.203
THE DRUG WASN'T
ON THE MARKET YET,

00:39:59.230 --> 00:40:00.730
SO IT WAS
VIRTUALLY UNTRACEABLE.

00:40:00.766 --> 00:40:02.226
YOU MUST HAVE BEEN DOSING
PAMELA FOR WEEKS,

00:40:02.267 --> 00:40:03.637
JUST WAITING FOR HER HEART
TO GIVE OUT.

00:40:03.669 --> 00:40:05.569
I WAS TRYING TO DO
THE RIGHT THING.

00:40:05.604 --> 00:40:08.374
WHY ELSE WOULD I CALL THE C.E.O.
OF THE COMPANY

00:40:08.406 --> 00:40:10.876
AND TELL HIM
ABOUT THE FALSIFIED RESULTS?

00:40:10.909 --> 00:40:12.079
YOU WERE WORRIED
THAT PAMELA FOUND OUT

00:40:12.110 --> 00:40:13.810
HER HUSBAND
WAS POISONING HER.

00:40:13.845 --> 00:40:16.075
IF SHE WENT TO THE POLICE,
YOU WOULD NEED A COVER STORY

00:40:16.114 --> 00:40:17.424
TO EXPLAIN WHY YOU HAD GIVEN HIM
THE PILLS,

00:40:17.449 --> 00:40:19.589
SO YOU PRETENDED
TO BE A WHISTLE-BLOWER.

00:40:19.618 --> 00:40:21.648
NO.
THAT IS NOT RIGHT.

00:40:21.687 --> 00:40:23.317
NO, WHAT'S NOT RIGHT

00:40:23.354 --> 00:40:26.024
IS THAT PAMELA WEILMAN WAS
ACCUSED OF KILLING HER HUSBAND

00:40:26.057 --> 00:40:27.827
WHEN IN FACT
YOU AND YOUR BOYFRIEND

00:40:27.859 --> 00:40:29.859
WERE TRYING TO KILL HER.

00:40:34.766 --> 00:40:36.466
I WANT A LAWYER.

00:40:36.502 --> 00:40:38.202
GONNA NEED A GOOD ONE.

00:40:40.205 --> 00:40:42.505
Gerard:
NICE WORKING WITH YOU, DOC.

00:40:51.316 --> 00:40:53.816
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

00:40:55.386 --> 00:40:57.986
Karyn: YOU WANTED TO SEE ME,
PROFESSOR?

00:40:58.023 --> 00:41:01.593
KARYN, YES.
UH, COME IN, PLEASE.

00:41:01.627 --> 00:41:04.757
UM, I-I WANTED
TO APOLOGIZE

00:41:04.796 --> 00:41:07.266
FOR WHAT I SAID ON THE COMMON
THE OTHER DAY.

00:41:07.298 --> 00:41:08.868
IT WAS -- IT WAS,
UH, HIGHLY INAPPROPRIATE

00:41:08.900 --> 00:41:13.640
AND, UH, UH,
OFFENSIVE.

00:41:13.672 --> 00:41:15.512
AND VERY PERCEPTIVE.

00:41:18.544 --> 00:41:21.514
I'M SORRY MY FRIEND
WAS SUCH A [BLEEP]

00:41:21.547 --> 00:41:25.117
I TOLD HER NOT TO FILE
THAT COMPLAINT.

00:41:25.150 --> 00:41:30.720
OH, OH, UH, UH,
COULD YOU --

00:41:30.756 --> 00:41:33.486
COULD YOU JUST WAIT --
UH, WAIT HERE ONE SECOND?

00:41:35.160 --> 00:41:36.290
LEWICKI!

00:41:36.327 --> 00:41:38.027
W-WHAT IS IT, DOC?

00:41:38.063 --> 00:41:41.333
I NEED YOU TO TELL ME IF
THERE'S SOMEONE IN MY OFFICE.

00:41:45.436 --> 00:41:47.566
Karyn: HEY!

00:41:53.478 --> 00:41:55.478
THAT ONE
WAS DEFINITELY REAL.

00:41:57.949 --> 00:42:01.419
Daniel: LAST WEEK, I ASKED,
"WHAT IS REALITY?"

00:42:01.452 --> 00:42:06.322
THIS WEEK,
I WANT TO TALK ABOUT NORMALCY.

00:42:06.357 --> 00:42:09.057
WHAT IS NORMAL?

00:42:09.094 --> 00:42:13.574
IF YOU FEEL SAD, DO YOU JUST
HAVE A CASE OF THE BLUES,

00:42:13.599 --> 00:42:17.539
OR ARE YOU SUFFERING
FROM A NEUROCHEMICAL IMBALANCE?

00:42:19.705 --> 00:42:22.665
THE VAST MAJORITY
OF THE CASE STUDIES

00:42:22.708 --> 00:42:24.308
THAT WE'VE BEEN LOOKING AT

00:42:24.342 --> 00:42:26.812
INVOLVE PATIENTS WHOSE BRAINS
ARE ANYTHING BUT NORMAL,

00:42:26.845 --> 00:42:29.005
AND THERE'S NO QUESTION
THEY SUFFER.

00:42:29.047 --> 00:42:32.847
BUT...

00:42:32.884 --> 00:42:34.854
IS IT ALL BAD?

00:42:34.886 --> 00:42:38.186
FOR SOME,
THEIR NEUROLOGICAL STATES

00:42:38.223 --> 00:42:40.063
MIGHT ACTUALLY PROTECT THEM

00:42:40.091 --> 00:42:43.961
FROM PAINFUL TRUTHS THAT NO ONE
WOULD WANT TO THINK ABOUT.

00:42:43.995 --> 00:42:47.465
OTHERS DEVELOP
A-A CHEERFUL DISPOSITION

00:42:47.498 --> 00:42:49.528
THAT MAY HELP THEM COPE
WITH SITUATIONS

00:42:49.567 --> 00:42:51.567
THE REST OF US
WOULD FIND DISTURBING.

00:42:54.505 --> 00:42:57.735
AND IF WE ARE TO ESTABLISH
A BASELINE,

00:42:57.776 --> 00:42:59.746
THEN WE ALSO
HAVE TO ASK OURSELVES

00:42:59.778 --> 00:43:02.308
HOW THE BRAINS OF EVEN
SO-CALLED NORMAL PEOPLE

00:43:02.347 --> 00:43:05.747
RESPOND TO CERTAIN STIMULI.

00:43:19.364 --> 00:43:21.934
AND IF WE'RE ABLE TO
TREAT THOSE PEOPLE

00:43:21.967 --> 00:43:24.367
LIVING WITH
NEUROLOGICAL DISORDERS,

00:43:24.402 --> 00:43:28.872
RESTORE THEM TO --
QUOTE -- "NORMALCY,"

00:43:28.907 --> 00:43:31.877
WELL, OF COURSE
WE'RE HELPING THEM.

00:43:31.910 --> 00:43:36.010
BUT MIGHT WE SOMETIMES
ALSO BE STRIPPING AWAY

00:43:36.047 --> 00:43:38.277
WHAT MAKES THEM UNIQUE...

00:43:39.818 --> 00:43:44.458
...ROBBING THEM
OF AN ESSENTIAL PART

00:43:44.489 --> 00:43:47.189
OF WHO THEY ARE?

00:44:25.230 --> 00:44:27.730
[ CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYS ]

